.................... // As defined in the following structure the pin connection is as follows: 
.................... //     D0  enable 
.................... //     D1  rs 
.................... //     D2  rw 
.................... //     D4  D4 
.................... //     D5  D5 
.................... //     D6  D6 
.................... //     D7  D7 
.................... // 
.................... //   LCD pins D0-D3 are not used and PIC D3 is not used. 
